        <TextBlock x:Name="textBlock" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Background="Azure" Margin="27,51,0,-24.6" TextWrapping="Wrap" Text="Hotel Administration System is a software created for improving experience of managing hotel business. This application gives user ability to keep at fingerprint all necessary information about his or her own business. This tools will increase your staff work performance. Any type of work can be conducted with this application, managing client database, booking a room, or calculating income" VerticalAlignment="Top" Height="223" Width="370" FontSize="16"/>
